(739, 1, 'Adi Poonguyile  ', 'Mano, Minmini  ', 'aa : ati poonguyile poonguyile kelukanalakananaka\r\n    nee paattetuththa kaaranaththa kooru             (ati)\r\n    yaaritaththil un manasu pochchu\r\n    noolap pola un utampu aachchi           (ati)\r\npe : vattamittu suththum kanni veechchu   \r\n    vaaya vittu ponadhenna pechchu            (poong\r\naa : aaththangarai andhapuram aakkik kollavaa\r\n    andha akkaraikkum ikkaraikkum kottai katta vaa\r\npe : maaman kaiyil poovai thandhu sootik kollavaa\r\n    ati aasai ennum oonjal katti aatik kollavaa\r\naa : sollu sollu thittam enna solluvadhu kashtamaa\r\n    poththi poththi vaichchadhenna ennennamo ishtamaa\r\npe : koovaama koovuriye kukkoo kukkoo paattu\r\n    maaththaama maaththipputtaa sokku poti pottu\r\n							(yaari\r\npe : oorai ellaam sutri vandha oththaikkiliye\r\n    ippa oritaththil nindradhenna sollukkiliye\r\naa : sondha pandham yaarumindri vandha kiliye\r\n    oru sondha ippo vandhadhenna vaasal vazhiye\r\npe : veru vitta aalangannu maamana thota paarkkudhu\r\n    maaman thotum aasaiyile mella mella pookkudhu\r\naa : pooppoovaa pookka vaichcha maaman avan yaaru\r\n    paatukira paattula thaan neeyum adhai kooru		(yaari\r\n', '5:07', '', '', '', 0, 0, '', ''),
(739, 2, 'Amman Kovil  ', 'Swarnalatha, Minmini  ', 'pe : amman koyil kumpam inge aativarum neramati\r\n    kumpangalai eththi vachchi kulavai ittu paatungati\r\npe : ammana koyil vaasalile\r\n    e .. ponganum ponganum pongasach choru\r\n    thanganum thanganum selvam nooru          (amman\r\npe : sakdhi neeye kaaliyammaa\r\n    pakdhi ulla makkalukku veliyammaa\r\n    undhan kungumaththa sooti vandhaa\r\n    mangalangal pongi varum vaazhkkaiyile\r\n    oorukkulla engalukku unna vittaa aaledhu\r\n    naanga unnai kumpitaadha naaledhu\r\n    poomikkulla ooththup pola pongi nirkum thaayammaa\r\n    saamikkulla nalla saami neeyammaa\r\nkuzhu : singam undhan vaakanandhaan engal thaaye\r\n    antam pintam engum ulla anpuththaaye\r\niru : ati pattith thotti ezhaikalai ratchippaaye      (amman\r\npe : enga nenjangal vaanaththile\r\n    rekka katti aatukira naalu idhu\r\n    ingu vanjangale edhumille nallavanga vaazhukira\r\n                                      ooru idhu\r\n    maadham ingu moonu mazhai peyya venum thannaale\r\n    panjam indri vaazha venum unnaale\r\n    thekki vaichcha aasaiyellaam seekkiraththile eetera\r\n    nalla vazhi kaatti vitu munnera\r\nkuzhu : mannulakam suththi varum thannaththaane\r\n     enga vaazhvum suththi varum unnaiththaane\r\niru : ati puththi tharum siththi tharum kompuththene        (amman\r\n', '5:02', '', '', '', 0, 0, '', ''),
(739, 3, 'En Thai Yennum  ', 'Illayaraja  ', 'aa  : en thaayennum koyilai kaakka marandhitta\r\n	paaviyati kiliye en vaayum vayiraiyum potri\r\n   	valarththitta paaviyati kiliye			     (en\r\n	enna thottaalum paarththaalum thoshamati kiliye\r\n      enakku ezhezhu jenmaththilum motcham illaikiliye\r\n                         		           (en\r\n      puththamadhi sollaiyile thattich chendra paaviyati\r\n 	vittu vittup pona pinne vekudhu en aaviyati    (puththi\r\n	ototi paatuppatten naalellaam yaar yaarkko\r\n	seraamal ponadhati serththadhu thaayaarukke\r\n	petra manam enna vendru thonaliye\r\n	pokaiyile solli vittu pokaliye\r\n	ini aatritavum thetritavum annaip pola yaaru   (en\r\n 	than vayitrai pattini pottu ennuyirai valarththavale\r\n	thannandhaniyaai irundhu ennaikkaraich cherththavale   (en\r\n	noyaale naan patuththaa nompirukkum aaththaa\r\n	thee moontu theerndhitumaa nam kanakku aaththaa\r\n	petravala thalli vachcha paavaththukku\r\n	pakkam vandhu kolli vaikka kootaliye\r\n	ennai aatritavum thetritavum\r\n	annaippola yaaru                           (en\r\nn\r\n', '4:54', '', '', '', 0, 0, '', ''),
