(817, 1, 'Anandha Kuyilin2  ', 'Arunmozhi, Bhavadharani  ', 'aa    :  aanandha kuyilin paattu thinam engalin veettukkulle....\r\n        pookkalil nanaiyum kaatru thinam engalin thottaththile\r\n        kilikalin koontukkulle pudhu ulakam pirandhadhe\r\n        anpu konta nenjikkulle oru vaanam virindhadhe\r\nkuzhu    : kanikal thiththippaa kavidhai thiththippaa\r\n        adhu anpai vita thiththippaa                      (aanandha)\r\naa     : poomi engum kantadhillai paasaththai un pole\r\npe     : veredhuvum thevaiyillai anpukku munnaale\r\naa     : nenjikkulle poo malarum veettukkul vandhaale\r\npe     : nimmadhiyil kan malarum paattukkal thandhaale\r\naa     : in;tha sondhangal podhume engal inpangal kootume\r\npe     : anpenum theyvam etriya veetum theyvaththin aalayamdhaan\r\nkuzhu    : veetu endraal motcham enpaar veetu andro nesaththile\r\npe     : thakkajudhakka thaam thaam thajnu thajnu thaam thakkajunu thakka thaam thaam\r\npe     : sailens                              kuzhu: atengappaa\r\npe     : sh...\r\npe     : anpinile anpinile aalayam kantene\r\n        annankalin kaikalile theepamum naandhaane\r\nkuzhu    : paasaththile vaasam tharum poovanam needhaane\r\n        nesaththile raakam tharum veenanayum needhaane\r\npe     : silar vedham paatalaam silar keedhai thetalaam\r\n        naan kanta vedham naan kanta keedham\r\n        annanin vaarththaikaldhaan\r\nkuzhu    : vaanin nilaa theyndhitalaam paasanilaa theyndhitumo      (aanandha)\r\n', '1:50', '', '', '', 0, 0, '', ''),
